Design Sprints, Safaris + Workshops

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"]

11 years of product building, 7 acquisitions of ideas we’ve built + over 353 projects.

We know the best way to build good sh*t. Tap into the experience + insight that’s created hundreds of products. Make our team part of your team, offering solutions + opinions. For a day, week or months.

Rocksauce knows how to motivate people. You know your business. We collaborate to make something amazing. Since your problem is unique to you, how we start will be, too.

Participate, facillitate + validate

Design Sprints

Facilitation is so 2019, y’all. We’re all about full participation.

We’ve refined Design Sprints into three specific flavors that work hand-in-hand or individually, depending on your needs.

Rocksauce becomes a seamless part of your team to help you solve the problem. Facilitating the exercises + conversations for the group, but also being at the table with your team. Bringing in new ideas + being as opinionated as anyone else.

Diversity of thought matters. The right people in the right room, from the C-Level to customer support who know all the complaints. And expert product builders like us.

[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"]


  • Alpha Sprint

    Start something new. Tailored to promote discovery + ideation.



  • Iteration Sprint

    Take existing ideas + continue to add features or grow the product.



  • Preparation Sprint

    Fill-in-gaps, answer questions + get stuff ready for production.

[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url="https://rsv9.local/2021/04/29/design-sprint-in-1-minute/" button_text="Click to keep learning about our Design Sprints" module_class="btn-orange-alt" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_image src="https://rsv9.local/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/design-workshops5.png" title_text="design-workshops5" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="section-testimonial" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_4,3_4" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="1_4" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_image src="https://rsv9.local/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/rocksauce_client_jodi_frank_culineer_recipe_app-1.png" title_text="rocksauce_client_jodi_frank_culineer_recipe_app 1" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="3_4" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"]

Jodi Frank, CEO of Cullineer

Observe, understand + create

Design Safaris

We come to you to dive head-first into the problem.

Sometimes, the problem is so big that a Design Sprint is too small. Existing business customers, with products in the market or with their own internal systems, can’t stop their lives to get everyone into the same room for 16 or more hours.

Nuance + environment matter. Our researchers + designers sit with your people, ask them questions, see how folks in the real-world are handling problems or difficulties. We identify the key internal experts, then come out and get going!

That’s the fuel we use to build you something remarkable.

[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text="Click to see if a Safari is right for you" module_class="btn-orange-alt" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="text-image-workshop" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"]

Discover, align + innovate

Innovation Workshops

Alignment is the cornerstone of any solution. Doesn’t matter if it’s a mobile app, a software platform, or a process that’s gonna revolutionize your production line.

A team running in different directions never reaches the goal. Products can’t be everything to everyone. Your team has to agree on what you’re doing + how you’re getting it done.

Rocksauce makes sure the best idea - not the loudest voice - drives the solution. We participate, serving the vital roles of user advocate, design expert + facilitator.

[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text="Click to book your a Workshop " module_class="btn-orange-alt" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_image src="https://rsv9.local/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/design-workshops7.png" title_text="design-workshops7" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="workshop-banner" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default" background_image="https://rsv9.local/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/design-workshops8.jpg" parallax="on"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.0" _module_preset="default"]
